reviewText: My kids love Franklin. This dvd has a ton of episodes on it which I really like. We haven't made it all the way through the dvd yet but so far all really cute and just what I'd  expect from Franklin, we love it!

We love Franklin and have several dvd's.
The episode on this disc are:
* Franklin and the Bus Patrol
* Franklin Loses a Book
* Franklin's Jug Band
* Franklin in Two Places
* Franklin the Teacher
* Franklin's Sailboat
* Franklin the Trooper
* Franklin Camps Out
* Franklin's Maple Syrup
* Franklin Plays Golf
* Franklin's Robot
* Franklin's Shell Trouble
* Franklin's Father
* Franklin's Rival
Several of them have Harriet in them which my youngest just loves.
why don`t they list the episodes that come on it online ?  so that makes me not know if I already have them
